- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with classifying legal documents and retrieving relevant information from them. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper uses machine learning techniques to classify text. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with legal documents and their classification, which has societal implications.
